#################
################# Start of all the settings

# KEY DEFINITIONS TO REMEMBER
# $mod = Set below
# Mod4 = Super key
# Mod1 = ALT key
# Control = CTRL key
# Shift = SHIFT key
# Escape = ESCAPE key
# Return = ENTER or RETURN key
# KP_Enter = Keypad Enter
# Pause = PAUSE key
# Print = PRINT key
# Tab = TAB key

################# what key binding in config
# Super + s/b/z
# Super+Control+ 
# 533   Super+Control+ o == Obsidian
# 534   Super+Control+ c == VScode
# 534   Super+Control+ b == bluebery


#       Super+ALT+b  New windown horizontal this is defaul
#       Super+Alt+v  Virtical

################# Define the $mod variable/key
# Disable autostart picom
# 775   Ctrl+Alt+o       == Picom Toogle
# A
# b
# c
# Key to rule them all : Super(Windows) or Alt key - see definition above
# set Super key
set $mod Mod4

################# Define the movements keys - variables

# This is setup for qwerty
# set $right to m if using azerty keyboard
set $up k
set $down j
set $left h
# set $right semicolon 
set $right l 

